index.richContent:
&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the &lt;strong&gt;üå¥ Jungle&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;what-is-this&quot;&gt;What is this?&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#what-is-this&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I‚Äôve been using &lt;a href=&quot;https://obsidian.md/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Obsidian&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for some time already and I found it to be a great place for storing information in a loosely-manner, so it can be retrieved at a later time. I was thinking about publishing my notes for some time, but I wanted to do so in a more controlled way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also, I‚Äôve been toying with an idea to add recipes and short notes sections to my &lt;a href=&quot;https://madebyme.today/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;website&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Frankly, I lacked the motivation to create new subpage templates with the necessary functionality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Meet &lt;strong&gt;üå¥ Jungle&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;what-is-jungle&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;üå¥ Jungle&lt;/strong&gt; is mostly an experiment; it‚Äôs a &lt;a href=&quot;https://jzhao.xyz/posts/networked-thought&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;digital garden&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; of sorts. I‚Äôm planning to publish some of my Obsidian notes here, so that they can be easily accessed by me and my friends, on any device. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;why-not-publish-on-madebymetoday&quot;&gt;Why not publish on &lt;a href=&quot;https://madebyme.today/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;madebyme.today&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#why-not-publish-on-madebymetoday&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I‚Äôve established an unwritten contact between me and my readers ‚Äî &lt;a href=&quot;https://madebyme.today/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;madebyme.today&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is for tech-related articles. I feel like if I‚Äôd publish a TTRPG session log or a cinnamon roll recipe on my website, I‚Äôd break that contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Think of it like this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://madebyme.today/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;madebyme.today&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is only for tech,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;üå¥ Jungle&lt;/strong&gt; is &lt;em&gt;not&lt;/em&gt; only for tech ‚Äî it is more Kamil.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;what-can-i-find-here&quot;&gt;What can I find here?&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#what-can-i-find-here&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Who knows? ¬Ø\_(„ÉÑ)_/¬Ø&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The notes are &lt;em&gt;kind of&lt;/em&gt; unstructured ‚Äî I‚Äôll put here anything I‚Äôm willing to share with the internet ‚Äî and only marginally reviewed before publishing, so you can expect typos and 404s.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;is-it-published-with-obsidian-publish&quot;&gt;Is it published with Obsidian Publish?&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#is-it-published-with-obsidian-publish&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://obsidian.md/publish&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Obsidian Publish&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is a great tool, but it does not allow you to fully customise the static website it produces. For this project I‚Äôve decided to go with &lt;a href=&quot;https://quartz.jzhao.xyz/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Quartz&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jzhao.xyz/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Jacky&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Quartz is a static-site generator ‚Äî like &lt;a href=&quot;https://gohugo.io/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Hugo&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ‚Äî but it was built with Obsidian in mind; it handles &lt;a href=&quot;https://quartz.jzhao.xyz/features/wikilinks&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Wikilinks&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://quartz.jzhao.xyz/features/callouts&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Callouts&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and many other Obsidian features out-of-the-box.&lt;/p&gt;
